OL,4,CLorry driver shortage threatens Haribo
OL,5,Csweets
OL,6, German confectionery giant Haribo has
OL,7, said it is struggling to deliver its
OL,8, sweets to shops in the UK because of a
OL,9, shortage of lorry drivers.
OL,11,FIt said that like many other producers
OL,12,Fand retailers, it was "experiencing
OL,13,Fchallenges" that were hitting supplies.
OL,15,FThe haulage industry has blamed the
OL,16,Fpandemic and Brexit for thousands of
OL,17,Funfilled HGV driver jobs.
OL,19,FThe government said it had taken
OL,20,Faction, by increasing HGV driving test
OL,21,Fcapacity and funding apprenticeships.
